lots of oil
onions and chili in beginning, let it fry, 1 spoon of ginger garlic, 1.5 spoon of chili powder, 1/5 spoon of turmeric, 1-2 spoons of
coriander powder, add fish curry masala to it. 4 to 1 ratio of onions to tomatoes. Once onion is fried, add tomatoes, add to blender. Then
on the side can make an okra fry. Then add this to the kadai.  
